Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US-Libya missile battle
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xprb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Mar 1986
Political storm follows naval battle between US and Libya in Gulf of Sidra. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.